<inglise> (a) all ships, including fishing vessels and recreational craft, irrespective of their flag, calling at, or operating within, a port of a Member State, with the exception of any warship, naval auxiliary or other ship owned or operated by a State and used, for the time being, only on government non-commercial service; and </inglise>
<eesti> a) k&otilde;igi laevade, sealhulgas kalalaevade ja l&otilde;bus&otilde;idulaevade suhtes, kes k&uuml;lastavad liikmesriigi sadamat v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;tavad seal, olenemata sellest, millise lipu all nad s&otilde;idavad, v&auml;lja arvatud s&otilde;jalaevad, merev&auml;e abilaevad v&otilde;i muud laevad, mis kuuluvad riigile v&otilde;i mida kasutatakse ainult riiklikel mittekaubanduslikel eesm&auml;rkidel, ja </eesti>
<inglise> (b) all ports of the Member States normally visited by ships falling under the scope of point (a). </inglise>
