<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> An appropriate waste reception and handling plan shall be developed and implemented for each port following consultations with the relevant parties, in particular with port users or their representatives, having regard to the requirements of Articles 4, 6, 7, 10 and 12. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga sadama jaoks t&ouml;&ouml;tatakse p&auml;rast asjaomaste isikutega, eelk&otilde;ige sadama kasutajate v&otilde;i nende esindajatega konsulteerimist v&auml;lja ja viiakse ellu asjakohane j&auml;&auml;tmete vastuv&otilde;tmise ja k&auml;itlemise kava, v&otilde;ttes arvesse artikleid 4, 6, 7, 10 ja 12. </eesti>
<inglise> Detailed requirements for the development of such plans are set out in Annex I. </inglise>
