<inglise> - improve the identification of ships which have not delivered their ship-generated waste and cargo residues in accordance with this Directive, </inglise>
<eesti> - t&otilde;hustada selliste laevade identifitseerimist, mis ei ole laevaheitmeid ja lastij&auml;&auml;tmeid k&auml;esoleva direktiivi kohaselt &uuml;le andnud, </eesti>
<inglise> - ascertain whether the goals set in Article 1 of the Directive have been met. </inglise>
